        <p>If you have a list of items (a list of car names, for example), storing the cars in single variables could look like this:</p>
        <script>
          str1= '<i> Volvo'+ '<br>' + 'BMW' +'<br>'+'Toyota </i> ' 
           document.write(str1 )
        </script>
